Responsibilities:

  Analyse usage data to determine trends and insights ona B2C portal
  Create hypotheses and actionable test scenarios for discovered insights
  Develop pilot frameworks to collaborate with internal and external stakeholders to conduct validation of hypothesis
  Distill bite-sized PR/content pieces based on the trends analysis that can be adapted for public consumption
  Develop partnerships with external industry partners to further the efficacy of industry education and best practices

Other Information:

  The duration of the traineeship is 6 months
